	"  Danger: Will cause most NPCs to move away from the position of the sound\n" +
	"  Bullet Impact: \n" +
	"  Carcass: \n" +
	"  Meat: \n" +
	"  Garbage: \n" +
	"  Thumper: causes antlions to run away briefly\n" +
